<div id="imageContent35eff3c0f26d4d54b0474101a4438fa7">
</div>
<h3 id="member16">Caroline Wiltshire and Nathan Norris</h3>
<p><em>Youth Support Coordinator</em></p>
<div>
<p>We provide a wide range of cognitive, recreational, and social activities for patients to participate in, which occupy and enable young people with cancer to develop, be empowered and deal with diagnosis whilst receiving treatment in the 3 hospitals covered by the service.</p>
</div>
<p>We actively encourage and support social interactions between patients and their families, close friends and other patients within the units, by organising activities both in and out of the hospital.</p>
<p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto: "> </a></p>
</div>
<div class="staff-info pad">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
