<div class="staff-title pad">
<div id="imageContentb20ccbaf4abc422db104871b805edb43">
</div>
<h3 id="member12">Jan Siddall</h3>
<p><em>Teenage Cancer Trust Nurse Lead </em></p>
<p>Jan is Nurse Lead for TYA patients, and has had many years experience in cancer and palliative care. Managing a service and caring for patients in this age range is both challenging and hugely rewarding. The team in Sheffield are highly motivated and aspire to give a very high standard of care to patients, and support their families and carers. We cover the North Trent region and parts of Yorkshire and Humberside. We as a team aim to make the patients cancer experience as comfortable as possible.</p>
<p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:Janice.siddall@sth.nhs.uk">Janice.siddall@sth.nhs.uk</a></p>
</div>
<div class="staff-info pad">
<h4>Qualifications</h4>
<p>MA (ed), BA Hons, RN,SCM, NDN</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
